data.text:
Beans are an edible item in bunker.jpeg. It appears as a can filled with beans. Using the beans will result in your character eat the beans using a spoon. While eating the beans, your face will be replaced with an exclusive face decal that stays on your face until your finished eating the beans or you unequip the item.

Trivia[]

the item was made by ROBLOX themselves.

On the catalog it costs 55 robux.
